+# P4.1 Latency Contract External Coverage
+
+## Goal
+Close latency-contract gaps for services not present in this archive:
+- Go ingest writer for `ingest_to_redis`
+- NestJS WS gateway writer for `emit_to_ws` and final `end_to_end_event`
+
+## Required owner-stage matrix
+- `go_ingest / ingest_to_redis`
+- `python_worker / redis_to_feature`
+- `python_worker / feature_to_emit`
+- `nest_gateway / emit_to_ws`
+- `nest_gateway / end_to_end_event`
+
+## Redis keys
+`metrics:latency_contract:last:<service>:<stage>:<symbol>`
+
+## SLO gate summary
+`metrics:latency_contract:slo:last`
+
+## Rollout
+1. Deploy Python P4 + P4.1 exporter/gate.
+2. Integrate Go writer from `integrations/go_ingest_latency_writer_v1.go`.
+3. Integrate Nest writer from `integrations/nest_ws_latency_writer_v1.ts`.
+4. Start `latency_contract_slo_gate_v1.py`.
+5. Alert on missing/stale coverage.
